paleta
________________________________________________________________________________

Change terminal colors on the fly independent of terminal emulator.


requirements
________________________________________________________________________________

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                              |
|  1. C99                                                                      |
|  2. POSIX C library                                                          |
|  3. A terminal with 'ESC ] 10;Pt ST', 'ESC ] 11;Pt ST', etc                  |
|                                                                              |
|  terminal support                                                            |
|                                                                              |
|  - st         patch       ./misc/st-osc_10_11_12-20200418-66520e1.patch      |
|  - hyper      clueless    https://github.com/vercel/hyper/issues/2038        |
|  - alacritty  good        https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty/issues/656  |
|  - vte        good        1a651cf990e67c4046fbff7674249259bcaa89a8           |
|  - xterm      good                                                           |
|  - urxvt      good                                                           |
|                                                                              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


build
________________________________________________________________________________

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                              |
|  $ make                                                                      |
|  $ make DESTDIR="" PREFIX="" install                                         |
|                                                                              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


usage
________________________________________________________________________________

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                              |
|                                                                              |
|  1. Setting the colorscheme.                                                 |
|                                                                              |
|     $ paleta < palettes/solarized-dark > ~/current_palette                   |
|                                                                              |
|                                                                              |
|     Input is [#]000000\\n over stdin in the following order.                 |
|                                                                              |
|        1 <foreground>                                                        |
|        2 <background>                                                        |
|        3 <cursor>                                                            |
|        4 <color0>                                                            |
|        5 <color1>                                                            |
|        6 <color2>                                                            |
|                                                                              |
|       ...                                                                    |
|                                                                              |
|      259 <color256>                                                          |
|                                                                              |
|     Output over stdout is the resulting set of sequences.                    |
|                                                                              |
|                                                                              |
|  2. Making the colorscheme work with new terminals                           |
|                                                                              |
|                                                                              |
|     In your shell's startup file (.bashrc, .zshrc, etc).                     |
|                                                                              |
|        1                                                                     |
|        2 cat ~/current_palette                                               |
|        3                                                                     |
|                                                                              |
|     This is the path to the file containing the sequences as set above.      |
|                                                                              |
|                                                                              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
